reviews.review_text: Shade of Grey? Thanx Don.  This is a nice audience recording, though Jerry's guitar is low in the mix.  There is some rather delicate playing especially for the Women Are Smarter.  The He's Gone is very soft and a stand alone version.  I swear I hear Shade of Grey in the beginning of space before the Wheel develops.  I am Playing the Alabama>Greatest Story on my radio show this week.  My only Dead shows at BCT and I lost this show.  Peace.
